{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- apparently, they had been threatened already for deportation, because the elderly, you see.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everywhere there was a connection to the elderly, or the ill, or the mentally unbalanced, or 'flawed' human beings in addition to being Jews-- were rounded up constantly, and earlier than the workforce, like my parents who were in forced labor who were useful working for Graf Zeppelin-- my mother and my father-- for a spare in some department.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Manual work, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Levents-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] lost my thread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had gone in earlier because they had been listed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they made themselves disappear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was assumed they'd been deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two, and then we three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, quietly in socks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, there were all these kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had to eat during certain hours because we didn't want to burn that electric light that was there, for fear that somebody would see that there's a light on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Light was a-- energy was a shortage, and besides-- eventually, I mean, even by then, there were threats of the air raids being attracted by lights.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father read, and believe it or not, my father knitted during that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People didn't entertain their children--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in that world, or in any of those worlds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you just played however you play.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I must tell you of a bizarre game we used to play on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These children that I referenced as having been removed from the kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to play a game called [GERMAN], and that word means 'rounding up.'",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we must have known something, we children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we would agree.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
